Description :

Leela is a 2016 Malayalam satirical film directed and produced by Ranjith for Capitol Theatre, starring Biju Menon in lead role. Vijayaraghavan, Suresh Krishna, Indrans, Sudheer Karamana, Parvathy Nambiar, Jagadish, and Priyanka does other supporting roles in the film. The soundtracks and background scores of the movie is composed by Bijibal.
